"{\"uid\": \"cnn.com-2024-07-24-sport-olympic-opening-ceremony-striking-dancers-spt-intl\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Follow: Hundreds of dancers threatening to disrupt theOlympic Games'Opening Ceremony over pay have called off strike action after reaching an agreement with Paris 2024, according to a statement from the union representing the dancers.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9616269514969553e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hundreds\", \"from\": 8, \"to\": 16}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 20, \"to\": 27}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 61}, {\"ngram\": \"Ceremony\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"pay\", \"from\": 90, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"strike action\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 123}, {\"ngram\": \"an agreement\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 151}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 193}, {\"ngram\": \"the union\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 208}, {\"ngram\": \"the dancers\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FSA-CGT union said on Wednesday that it received a \\\"final offer\\\" from Paris 2024 and their employers, proposing to increase payment for broadcasting performance rights for everyone.\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"FSA-CGT union\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 268}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"final offer\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 300}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"their employers\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"payment\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"performance rights\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Related articleThe Olympic Games face a unique set of potential security threats in Paris.\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999993453912, \"rank\": 6.545996396253326e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Related articleThe Olympic Games\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique set\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"potential security threats\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers say everyone will be safe On Monday, some 220 dancers stopped a rehearsal along the banks of Paris' River Seine - along which the Opening Ceremony is due to take place - to protest inequalities in pay and housing conditions between the dancers.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999993453912, \"rank\": 6.545996396253326e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.6466148133969555, \"rank\": 0.5391656006149198, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organizers\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"some 220 dancers\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"a rehearsal\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"inequalities\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"pay and housing conditions\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"the dancers\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A representative for the union previously told CNN that the ceremony was \\\"in danger\\\" after a protest and possible strike action by more than 200 dancers due to take part in Friday'sceremony, a union representative for the dancers told CNN Tuesday.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 816, \"end\": 819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9997892715959005, \"rank\": 0.00021072382280193637, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9997892715959005, \"rank\": 0.00021072382280193637, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A representative\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"the union\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"danger\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"a protest\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 869}, {\"ngram\": \"possible strike action\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 200 dancers\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday'sceremony\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"a union representative\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"the dancers\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The ceremony is in danger in a sense, yes.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ceremony\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"danger\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it will depend on solidarity because the strike is an individual decision,\\\" Lucie Sorin, a delegate for the FSA-CGT union, previously told CNN.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9997892715959005, \"rank\": 0.00021072382280193637, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"solidarity\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"the strike\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual decision\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"Lucie Sorin\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"a delegate\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"the FSA-CGT union\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said that the dancers were negotiating with Paris 2024 and their employers to obtain higher salaries and a sum of money for the \\\"most precarious\\\" performers.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1259, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9616269514969553e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dancers\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"higher salaries\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"a sum\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"most precarious\\\" performers\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the union said Wednesday added that \\\"in agreement with the artists concerned,\\\" it has decided \\\"to accept this proposal and to lift the strike notice for the ceremony on Friday July 26.\\\"\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the union\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"agreement\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"the artists\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"this proposal\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"the strike notice\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday July\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The union said that the outcome wasn't a total victory but that it met certain demands, in particular those of the dancers most at risk.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The union\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"a total victory\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"certain demands\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"in particular those\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"the dancers\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's Opening Ceremony will be the first ever held on a river.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1715, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource